BL_C_SITBI_Ever_Aborted_SA_stop_method: I was riding in a car and strongly considering jumping out of the door. The image kept playing in my mind of me unlocking the door, opening it, unbuckling my seatbelt and jumping. The images were so lifelike and strong, they had multiple endings: I skidded along the road, tearing skin, maybe a car would panic but not stop before they hit me. I was getting more and more afraid of following the thoughts out, as my body began to itch to just do it. So I forced myself to start a conversation about a video game I liked with my parents in order to force myself to think about something else. (For context, this was something I would almost never in any situation do since I don’t like to bother other people with my interests if they have no basis of what I’m talking about)
